# Model weights tracked via Git LFS (best.pt ~23 MB, best.onnx ~45 MB)
model/weights/*.pt filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
model/weights/*.onnx filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# Test fixtures are small — keep them in regular git so the backend test
# suite works on a fresh clone without pulling LFS objects.
backend/tests/fixtures/*.jpg -filter -diff -merge text=auto
